    "The latter forms a broad distribution centered around k = 0.The plan of the paper is the following.",
    "II, we introduce the model, define the observables under study, and describe the numerical methods employed.",
    "We also describe the application of perturbative techniques in limiting cases.",
    "Section III discusses the relaxation from an initial state with fully polarized local spins for a single charge carrier, with Sec.",
    "III B considering the situation with additional diagonal disorder."
